List Rekomendasi Ayam Goreng di Jogja (buat yg bosen Gudeg):

Ayam Goreng Ny Suharti (Asli, Foto Ibu Suharti) - buat yg doyan Ayam Goreng Asin dan Oily

Ayam Goreng Suharti (Gambar Ayam, punya ex-suami) - Taste similar to original but Less Salty, and less Oily.

Ayam Goreng Mbah Cemplung - Enak, Gurih, Ukuran Besar, tapi Alot.

Ayam Goreng Bu Tini - Ayam Goreng Bacem - this one is champion.
